name: "Little Diva" 8.5 x 11 in. Print
description:
This Little Diva has miles of style and attitude to match! She thinks she's pretty special which is a good thing..as long as she gets her way.

This print is meant to delight and inspire so let's give it up for Miss Thing!! It was created using colored pencils and bristol board paper. The print size is 8.5 x 11" and is printed on somerset velvet paper to retain the quality, texture and color of the original.

name: "Something's Fishy" 8.5 x 11 in. Print
description:
Cat and fish! A perfect combination, as long as they all stay where they're supposed to. Things look like they're gonna get interesting, don't they?

This print is meant to delight and inspire so give someone a big hug! It was created using colored pencils and bristol board paper. The print size is 8.5 x 11" and is printed on somerset velvet paper to retain the quality, texture and color of the original.

name: "Dancing Ducks" 8.5 x 11 in. Print
description: Four little ducks joyfully dancing in a row! Well, not quite four. You see, three feel the beat but number four has gotten sidetracked by a playful dragonfly. hopefully, your little one will dance along and enjoy many happy hours with these exhuberant duck babies! In bright yellows, brilliant orange, and hints of green and blue , it's sure to give a zing to your baby's room walls! This print is meant to delight and inspire. It was created using colored pencils, and watercolor markers on Strathmore watercolor paper. It is 8.5 x 11" and printed on thick matte paper to retain the texture of the original art.

name: "Ballerina" 8.5 x 11 in. Print
description:
Give your prima ballerina a reason to twirl on her toes. This little ballerina has a perfect place for me to personalize her name so that everyone will know who's the star in your ballet company! A pretty and soft combination of pinks, beige, pale yellow and browns, she'll wear out her toe shoes dancing to her hearts content. 

This original piece of art is meant to delight and inspire. It was created with colored pencils and watercolor markers on Strathmore Bristol paper. The print size is 8.5 x 11" and is done on thick, matte paper to retain the texture of the original art.

name: "Fairy Dreaming" 8.5 x 11 in. Print
description: Sweet little Amelia is dreaming about her lovely day as she flies over some fragrant flowers. Did she get into mischief or do some good deeds? Well, it's up to you and your child to invent a wonderful story about her day. This original piece of art is meant to delight and inspire. It was created with colored pencils on Strathmore watercolor paper. The print size is 8.5 x 11" and is done on thick, matte paper to retain the texture of the original art. It is first in my new series of Fairy art
